Country-Capital API

1.What is Country-Capital API?
The Country-Capital API is a simple RESTful API that takes a capital city name as input and returns the corresponding country name.
This API can be useful in various applications where country information is required.

2.Prerequisites:
To set up a local dev environment for the Country-Capital API, you will need to have the following installed on your system:
>Python 3.x
>pip

3.Contribution:
If you want to contribute to this project, please follow the steps below:

Fork this repository to your own GitHub account.
Create a new branch for your changes.
Make your changes and commit them to your branch.
Push your changes to your fork.
Create a pull request from your fork to this repository.
We welcome any contributions, including bug fixes, new features, and improvements to documentation.

